<div id="review_2794648060" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2794648060" />
    <a title="Dean" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/36924335-dean"><img alt="Dean" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2794648060?book_show_action=true">Apr 21, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dean" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dean" href="/user/show/36924335-dean">Dean</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2794648060" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer179816790266304752">An excellent study of the different views of freedom. Does an excellent job of demonstrating both sides of the issues of the civil war and the seeming reasonableness of the arguments. Very useful footnotes about what is real and not. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


