          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780385159036" href="/book/show/1823293.Freedom">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/17106786-kerrycat?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1333614628" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15010674553978120686">I took my sweet time with this 974 page bad boy, which now rivals my affection for the Shaaras as far as ACW fiction goes. With plenty of sources to back up this fictional account, which treats from mid-1861 to January 1, 1863, this is compelling drama that speaks to a reality that none of us read in our history books at school or beyond. An absolute masterpiece. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


